ActBusiness Development Bank of Canada Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister for International Trade of VIVEK JAIN of Regina, Saskatchewan, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Business Development Bank of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Michael Calyniuk, whose term has expired.
